{
  "stem": "21004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why you going to do that, take us to the commandos?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was raised on a village, and I lived in a village between Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told them a story about my mother, how she was helping, you know, people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they somehow think it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they say, eh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We let them go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they let me go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had yet tobacco hid in the barracks where my wife send me a pound of tobacco.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was more than money in the years in the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because there was no money-- no-- no cigarettes or whatever to get.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I say, here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a pound of tobacco.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll give you nice boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they say, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You a Jew, but you are not smart enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You should be smart not to go through a village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever you go, you want to go back to here or whatever you want to go, go in the back of the village around, and where there's no village you can go where the highway where nobody is going.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they gave me the idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No more going through a village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, when we went and we coming closer the fourth day, what's happened the fourth day already, what's happened, we were going through a-- there was a lake and there was a field where a guy was there, and we didn't see.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't spot him, by a tree.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was where they were-- he was feeding his horse there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was there with the horse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he jumped on us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Grabbed me and him, one with one hand and one with the other hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Grabbed us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You Jew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You-- you [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Ukrainian, [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
